description: Flip dinner on its head with this easy baked beans, salsa and cheese quesadilla recipe. This tasty meal is as fun to make as it is to eat.
keywords: Quesadilla,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Budget,Halal,High protein,High fibre,Vegetarian,Avocado,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Easy MexicanInspired Baked Bean Quesadillas Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 425g canned SPC baked beans in tomato sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Place tortillas on a flat surface. Evenly spoon baked beans over one half of each tortilla.
Sprinkle cheese over beans, then spoon over salsa. Season with pepper. Fold over tortilla to enclose filling.

Spray a large frying pan with oil and heat over mediumhigh heat. Cook tortillas, 2 at a time, for 2 minutes on each side, or until filling is heated through and cheese has melted. Repeat with remaining tortillas.
Cut tortillas into wedges and serve with avocado, coriander leaves and cracked pepper.
